Questions to be asked in chatbot to check the features 

Snapshot (labs + vitals + meds)
“Give a clinical snapshot for p1 including current labs, vitals, and active medications.”
​

“How is patient 3 doing right now? Summarize their condition with labs and vitals.”
​

“Show me a status snapshot of the currently selected patient with labs, vitals, and diagnosis.”
​

Medications + high‑risk drugs
“List all medications for p4 and highlight any high‑risk drugs I should be careful about.”
​

“For patient 2, show only their medications with doses and routes.”
​

“Are there any high‑risk medications for the current patient that need closer monitoring?”
​

Patient summary card / overall summary
“Provide a brief clinical summary for the currently selected patient without going into too much detail.”
​

“Switch to p6 and summarize their age, diagnosis, and current status in a few lines.”
​

Triage feature
“For p2, what is the triage level and which care setting do you recommend (OPD, ward, or ICU)?”
